item.content:encoded:
Truck Driver Easy Road is not only a truck free driving but also a hard-core parking simulation game with 3D game art animation. Whether you want to drive in this town on the map nor proceed with the parking lessons is fine. Get in the truck and enjoy Truck Driver Easy Road!
WASD or arrow keys – drive, C – change camera, Y – wipers, U – mud flaps, V – hand brake, M – map, Right mouse button – horn, Hold the left mouse button and drag – camera overview, P – pause, R – open the window on the left, B – look back, L – light

item.content:encoded:
Toy-Match is a matching-3 game. You can be relaxed in this game. The mission is to collect some directional things. It is easy, just match three or more same color blocks to a line. If you match the blocks with the background, it will collect them. When you collect all the props, you can continue the next level. But your moves are limited, you should better collect them before running out of moves. Sounds difficult? Do not be upset, we will mention you if you actually do not know how to move. Let us enjoy the game!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
One Cell is a solitaire card game. You can have fun in a poker game here. It is a little difficult, you have to match specific cards. The cards matching in numerical order, but only the different colors can match. This makes the game harder. But I believe you can solve this card puzzle by your wisdom. The Aces will be collected that can help you a little. Also, you can put a card to the free cell temporarily when you have no way to move the cards. Only you have three chances to undo the moves. If you can not figure out, only one thing you can do is restart.
drag to play

You are mastering a little coffee shop, learn how to manage it, and how the shop keeps running well. I will teach you how to make drinks, with your level up you could make more kinds of drinks. Customers will get more and more, their Purchase demand is also more strange, but you have to satisfy them. You will get busier, improve your equipment to cook faster, you can also upgrade the materials that earn more money! Collect keys to unlock more characters!
Click to cook

item.content:encoded:
Truck Loader Online Master is a cartoon-style 2D game. Players need to drive the truck to move back and forth, transport the goods to the designated location, and then deliver the container to the truck. It is worth noting that some levels have only one container, and most There are many containers in the level of, so players need to make good use of the magnet function to attach the goods to the iron products, and finally place the containers on the truck. This game requires great patience, wish you success!
use arrow keys and click the mouse to play.

item.content:encoded:
Mathematics is one of the most complex subjects in the world. The Nobel Prize in Mathematics is awarded to those outstanding mathematics masters every year. Do you think you are good at mathematics? Math Fun Solarize is a math-related game that can test your math ability. You need to answer these math questions as soon as possible and check the scores you can get before you make a mistake. Smart kids are always good at doing math problems. If you want to exercise your calculation skills, you might as well try this game!
Mouse click or tap the screen to play.

item.content:encoded:
Chinese Chess board game against a computer opponent. To win you need to capture the general of your opponent. Xiangqi, also called Chinese chess or Elephant chess, is a strategy board game for two players. It is one of the most popular board games in China. The game represents a battle between two armies, with the object of capturing the enemy’s general. Distinctive features of xiangqi include the cannon, which must jump to capture, a rule prohibiting the generals from facing each other directly, areas on the board called the river and palace, which restrict the movement of some pieces, and placement of the pieces on the intersections of the board lines, rather than within the squares.
Click and drag the mouse to play.

item.description: A daily traffic jam awaits you to clear it. Your goal is to make the police car slide through the exit by moving other cars. Move the cars and trucks up and down, left and right, until the road is cleared so the police car can get out of the exit. There are four difficulties […]
item.content:encoded:
A daily traffic jam awaits you to clear it. Your goal is to make the police car slide through the exit by moving other cars. Move the cars and trucks up and down, left and right, until the road is cleared so the police car can get out of the exit. There are four difficulties here and you can choose to add or not add walls to make the game more difficult. There is also a time timer to see how long you can help the police car get out of the exit.
Click to operate

item.content:encoded:

Fill the screen with balloons to open locks and release them. Remember the ballooning number has to be greater than the number behind it to pass the level. Come and play!
